{"tid":2156211,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【黎智英被捕】黎智英：勿買壹傳媒股票 公司基本因素無法支持升勢（第二版）","createTime":"2020-08-14T09:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T10:09:06.000Z","uid":28114,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1dba582ef3c8a2f23b75cd99d165b75e67432004","tid":2156211,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:43:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2724535?lcc=an\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2724535%3Flcc%3Dan&d=NZlAC2w8bMplDXSravNUcYT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=8cd02791\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2724535?lcc=an</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2720000/2724535/ckfn20200505201_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2720000%2F2724535%2Fckfn20200505201_1024_1024.jpg&h=b6a0fc44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒 （00282） 股價因於本周一、二炒起，引起證監會關注，並指壹傳媒出現異常升幅，呼籲投資者買賣壹傳媒股份時務須格外審慎。壹傳媒創辦人黎智英接受《彭博》訪問時警告，投資者不要買入壹傳媒的股票，因為壹傳媒的基本面無法支持最近的上漲趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n黎智英表示，收入很少的人希望透過買入壹傳媒股票表達憤怒及對壹傳媒的支持；當每個人都買了一點，就變得很多了並推高了股價。他又告訴人們「不要這麼做，不要這麼做，因為你會虧錢的」<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒周一、二炒起後連跌兩日，今日有所反彈，最多曾升約37%，全日收報0.4元，升幅收窄至5.3%，成交額2.1億元。"},{"pid":"976602aaa48101310330655dafd381f958d3253f","tid":2156211,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:46:18.000Z","msg":"CCTai益晒班炒家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9f3e7a9bcb9bcf630b357dc129211551eb9658","tid":2156211,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:47:44.000Z","msg":"買蘋果係買佢理念道德, 邊個唔買都無資格有民主"},{"pid":"013a284de86969a9b1d9d96b3d1abe23f9f3550a","tid":2156211,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/d